snippet.title: FoxyLand Anniversary - PC Gameplay (Steam)
snippet.description:
The PC version is different from the Mega Drive (and Evercade) counterpart in some areas, namely you do not have a life limit and the cherries are used to buy optional headgear. It's also available on Switch, PS4 and Xbox One.

Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/718320/FoxyLand/

The MD version is also available on Indie Heroes Collection 1 for Evercade.
